                        Located in the northern part of the beautiful Greek island of Samothrace, this recently renovated holiday home is now available for rent.
                        Up to eight people can enjoy this lovely place.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        The house is divided into two parts: the ground floor has a large living area with huge balcony windows for a great view to the garden, a newly installed kitchen with a large refrigerator, oven, stovetop, and all the utilities to prepare your favorite meals or snacks. Furthermore, there are two cosy bedrooms, both equipped with king size beds. It has a separate bathroom with toilet, a large walk-in shower, built with tiny stones found around the island.  The main terrace has a typical Greek wood oven, available for a barbecue or pizza evening.
                    <p>
                        On the first floor, under the roof and reachable from the outside, there is a small loft for up to two to four people. It has a sleeping area with the same king size bed found downstairs, and a sitting area with a sofa bed.  The bathroom has a large bathtub and a toilet.  Top notch is the terrace with an almost 180 degrees view of the blue Aegean Sea in the front, and in the back the impressive Fengari Mountain.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        The large green garden with fruit and olive trees has a private swimming pool to cool down on hot days. This setting is said to be unique in Samothrace and both garden and pool will be maintained on a regular base during your stay.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Villa Monte Kariotes is available for rent now!
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Please <a href="#reservations" title="Make your reservation">contact</a> your hosts Christine or Barbara for pricing and availability or any other request you have. They will be happy to assist you.
